msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Raven veŇ°ńćine` za veŇ°ńćino, ki se je spremenila, s ńćimer "
"se prikaŇĺe spustni seznam vseh razpoloŇĺljivih ravni. Kliknite novo raven za "
"veŇ°ńćino. Ko je izbrana, se polje :guilabel:`Trenutno` ustrezno posodobi. "
"Nato kliknite v polje :guilabel:`Utemeljitev` za veŇ°ńćino in vnesite ustrezne "
"podrobnosti, ki pojasnjujejo spremembo, kot je `opravil test jezikovne "
"tekmovalnosti` ali `prejel certifikat Javascript`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/appraisals/new_appraisals.rst:187
msgid ""
"If necessary, :ref:`add any new skills <employees/skills>` for the employee."
msgstr "Po potrebi :ref:`dodajte nove veŇ°ńćine <employees/skills>` za kader."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/appraisals/new_appraisals.rst:189
msgid ""
"After the appraisal is completed and the skills have been updated, the next "
"time an appraisal is confirmed, the updated skills populate the *Skills* tab."
msgstr ""
"Ko je vrednotenje zakljuńćeno in so veŇ°ńćine posodobljene, se ob naslednjem "
