"PoiŇ°ńćite Ňĺelenega zaposlenega, nato kliknite ali tapnite njegovo kartico "
"Kanban. Zaposleni je samodejno prijavljen ali odjavljen glede na njegov "
"status v aplikaciji **Prisotnost**. Zaslon na kratko prikaŇĺe zaslon "
"*DobrodoŇ°li* ali *Nasvidenje* s trenutnim datumom in ńćasom ter vsemi "
"predhodno zabeleŇĺenimi urami prisotnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_onboarding.rst:47
msgid ""
"After the specified period of time designated in the :ref:`kiosk settings "
"<attendances/kiosk-settings>` has elapsed, the screen reverts to the main "
"*Onboarding* dashboard. To exit the screen sooner, click the :guilabel:`OK` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Ko preteńće dolońćeno ńćasovno obdobje, dolońćeno v :ref:`nastavitvah kioska "
"<attendances/kiosk-settings>`, se zaslon vrne na glavno nadzorno ploŇ°ńćo "
"*Onboarding*. Za hitrejŇ°i izhod iz zaslona kliknite gumb :guilabel:`V redu`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_onboarding.rst:52
msgid ""
"The list of departments on the left-side or the search bar at the top can be "
"used to navigate to the desired employee."
msgstr ""
"Za navigacijo do Ňĺelenega zaposlenega lahko uporabite seznam oddelkov na "
"levi strani ali iskalno vrstico na vrhu."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_onboarding.rst:58
msgid "Badge with barcode"
msgstr "Znańćka s ńćrtno kodo"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_onboarding.rst:60
msgid ""
"The second option available to check-in or check-out is to use an ID badge "
"that has a barcode on it. Click or tap on the center image above the "
"text :guilabel:`Badge with Barcode on Tablet`, and a dashboard loads "
"displaying two options: :guilabel:`Scan your badge` and :guilabel:`New Set-"
"up (Employee/Badge)`."
msgstr ""
"Druga moŇĺnost za prijavo ali odjavo je uporaba identifikacijske znańćke s "
"ńćrtno kodo. Kliknite ali tapnite na srednjo sliko nad "
"besedilom :guilabel:`Znańćka s ńćrtno kodo na tablici` in naloŇĺi se nadzorna "
"ploŇ°ńća, ki prikazuje dve moŇĺnosti: :guilabel:`Skeniraj svojo znańćko` "
"in :guilabel:`Nova nastavitev (Zaposleni/Znańćka)`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_onboarding.rst:65
msgid ""
"If the employee has an ID badge with a barcode, click the :guilabel:`Scan "
