#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/kiosks.rst:None
msgid "The pop-up that appears when prompted to enter a pin."
msgstr "Pojavno okno, ki se prikaŇĺe ob pozivu za vnos PIN-a."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/kiosks.rst:184
msgid "Confirmation message"
msgstr "Potrditveno sporońćilo"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/kiosks.rst:186
msgid ""
"When an employee checks in or out, a confirmation message appears, with all "
"the check-in or check-out information."
msgstr ""
"Ko se kader prijavi ali odjavi, se prikaŇĺe potrditveno sporońćilo z vsemi "
"informacijami o prijavi ali odjavi."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/kiosks.rst:189
msgid ""
"When checking in, the :guilabel:`Welcome (Employee)` message appears, along "
"with the current date and time. If the employee has already checked in and "
"out that day, an :guilabel:`Hours Previously Today: HH:MM` message also "
"appears, showing the total hours logged earlier."
msgstr ""
"Ob prijavi se prikaŇĺe sporońćilo :guilabel:`DobrodoŇ°li (Kader)` skupaj s "
"trenutnim datumom in ńćasom. ńĆe se je kader na ta dan Ňĺe prijavil in odjavil, "
"se prikaŇĺe tudi sporońćilo :guilabel:`Ure prej danes: HH:MM`, ki prikazuje "
"skupno Ň°tevilo ur, zabeleŇĺenih prej."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/kiosks.rst:193
msgid ""
"When checking out, :guilabel:`Goodbye (Employee)` appears, as well as the "
"date and time of checkout. Beneath the message is an :guilabel:`Hours Today: "
"HH:MM` field, with the total hours and minutes logged for the day."
msgstr ""
"Pri odjavi se prikaŇĺe :guilabel:`Nasvidenje (Kader)`, skupaj z datumom in "
"ńćasom odjave. Pod sporońćilom je polje :guilabel:`Ur danes: HH:MM` s skupnimi "
"urami in minutami, zabeleŇĺenimi za ta dan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/kiosks.rst:197
msgid ""
"Beneath both the \"welcome\" and \"goodbye\" messages is an :guilabel:`OK` "
"button. To exit the screen before the preset time in the kiosk, tap "
"the :guilabel:`OK` button."
msgstr ""
"Pod sporońćiloma \"dobrodoŇ°li\" in \"na svidenje\" je gumb :guilabel:`V "
"redu`. Za izhod z zaslona pred vnaprej dolońćenim ńćasom v kiosku tapnite "
"gumb :guilabel:`V redu`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/kiosks.rst:None
msgid "The goodbye message with all the employee's check out information."
msgstr "Sporońćilo na svidenje z vsemi podatki o odjavi kadra."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:3
msgid "Work approvals and overtime"
msgstr "Odobritve dela in nadurno delo"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo's **Attendances** app requires management oversight in order to ensure "
"all logged attendances are correct, especially overtime hours and incomplete "
"shifts."
msgstr ""
"Odoo aplikacija **Prisotnosti** zahteva nadzor vodstva, da so vsi zabeleŇĺeni "
"podatki o prisotnosti pravilni, zlasti nadurne ure in nedokonńćane izmene."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:11
msgid "Management dashboard"
msgstr "Nadzorna ploŇ°ńća vodstva"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:13
msgid ""
"All attendance records that require approval, typically due to overlapping "
"work entries or unapproved time off, are managed from a centralized "
"management dashboard. To access this, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Attendances app --> Management`."
msgstr ""
"Vsi zapisi prisotnosti, ki zahtevajo odobritev, obińćajno zaradi "
"prekrivajońćih se delovnih vnosov ali neodobrene odsotnosti, se upravljajo s "
"centralizirane nadzorne ploŇ°ńće vodstva. Za dostop pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Prisotnosti --> Vodstvo`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:17
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Management` dashboard only displays attendance records for "
"current employees that need to be approved, in a default list view. This is "
"due to the two default filters in the search bar, the :guilabel:`To Approve` "
"and :guilabel:`Active Employees`."
msgstr ""
"Nadzorna ploŇ°ńća :guilabel:`Vodstvo` prikazuje samo zapise prisotnosti za "
"trenutne kadre, ki jih je treba odobriti, v privzetem seznamskem pogledu. To "
"je posledica dveh privzetih filtrov v iskalni vrstici: :guilabel:`Za "
"odobritev` in :guilabel:`Aktivni kadri`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:21
msgid "Each attendance record displays the following information:"
msgstr "Vsak zapis prisotnosti prikazuje naslednje informacije:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:25
msgid ":guilabel:`Check Out`: The date and time the employee checked out."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Odjava`: Datum in ńćas, ko se je kader odjavil."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:26
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Worked Time`: The number of worked hours the employee logged."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Opravljeni ńćas`: Ň†tevilo opravljenih ur, ki jih je kader "
"zabeleŇĺil."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:27
msgid ":guilabel:`Worked Extra Hours`: The amount of overtime worked."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Opravljene dodatne ure`: Kolińćina opravljenih nadur."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:28
msgid ":guilabel:`Extra Hours`: The total approved extra hours."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Dodatne ure`: Skupne odobrene dodatne ure."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Attendances app Management dashboard, displaying entries needing "
"approval."
msgstr ""
"Nadzorna ploŇ°ńća Vodstvo aplikacije Prisotnosti s prikazom vnosov, ki "
"potrebujejo odobritev."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:36
msgid "Approvals and refusals"
msgstr "Odobritve in zavrnitve"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:38
msgid ""
"Attendance records can be approved and refused directly from "
"the :ref:`Management dashboard <attendances/dashboard>`. At the far-right of "
"each record, :icon:`fa-check` :guilabel:`Approve` and :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`Refuse` buttons appear. Click the corresponding button to "
"either approve or refuse the logged attendance record."
msgstr ""
"Zapise prisotnosti lahko odobrimo in zavrnemo neposredno z :ref:`Nadzorne "
"ploŇ°ńće vodstva <attendances/dashboard>`. Na skrajni desni strani vsakega "
"zapisa se prikaŇĺeta gumba :icon:`fa-check` :guilabel:`Odobri` in :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`Zavrni`. Kliknite ustrezen gumb za odobritev ali zavrnitev "
"zabeleŇĺenega zapisa prisotnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:44
msgid ""
"When approving or refusing attendance records from "
"the :guilabel:`Management` dashboard, it is **not** possible to view the "
"details of the attendance record."
msgstr ""
"Pri odobritvi ali zavrnitvi zapisov prisotnosti z nadzorne "
"ploŇ°ńće :guilabel:`Vodstvo` **ni** mogońće pregledati podrobnosti zapisa "
"prisotnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:48
msgid "Partial approvals"
msgstr "Delne odobritve"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:50
msgid ""
"It is possible to approve a portion of the logged :guilabel:`Extra Hours` "
"and not the full amount. To approve only a portion of overtime, click into "
"an attendance record to view the details."
msgstr ""
"Mogońće je odobriti del zabeleŇĺenih :guilabel:`Dodatnih ur`, ne pa celotnega "
"zneska. Za odobritev samo dela nadurnega dela kliknite na zapis prisotnosti "
"za ogled podrobnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:53
msgid ""
"The top half of the record displays the specific check in and check out "
"details, including the method used. The :guilabel:`Check In` "
"and :guilabel:`Check Out` information in the top half of the form can be "
"modified, if needed. Click into the desired field, and make any needed "
"changes."
msgstr ""
"Zgornja polovica zapisa prikazuje podrobnosti dolońćene prijave in odjave, "
"vkljuńćno z uporabljeno metodo. Informacije :guilabel:`Prijava` "
"in :guilabel:`Odjava` v zgornji polovici obrazca je mogońće po potrebi "
"spremeniti. Kliknite na Ňĺeleno polje in izvedite potrebne spremembe."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:57
msgid ""
"The bottom half of the form contains the *Overtime Details* tab. This tab "
"lists the overtime rules used to calculate the extra hours, along with the "
"pay rate and status. The extra hours listed in this tab can be modified, "
"allowing for partial overtime approval."
msgstr ""
"Spodnja polovica obrazca vsebuje zavihek *Podrobnosti nadur*. Ta zavihek "
"navaja pravila nadur, uporabljena za izrańćun dodatnih ur, skupaj s plańćilno "
"stopnjo in statusom. Dodatne ure, navedene v tem zavihku, je mogońće "
"spremeniti, kar omogońća delno odobritev nadur."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:61
msgid ""
"Click into the :guilabel:`Extra Hours (encoded)` field of the line being "
"modified. Enter the amount of hours being approved in an `HH:MM` format, "
"then click :icon:`fa-check` :guilabel:`Approve` at the end of the line."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite v polje :guilabel:`Dodatne ure (kodirane)` v vrstici, ki se "
"spreminja. Vnesite Ň°tevilo ur, ki se odobrava, v formatu `HH:MM`, nato "
"kliknite :icon:`fa-check` :guilabel:`Odobri` na koncu vrstice."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:None
msgid "A detailed attendance record."
msgstr "Podroben evidenńćni zapis prisotnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:68
msgid ""
"After editing and approving the :guilabel:`Extra Hours (encoded)` field, the "
"status changes to :guilabel:`Approved`, and the :guilabel:`Extra Hours` "
"field in the top half of the form updates to display the approved overtime."
msgstr ""
"Po urejanju in odobritvi polja :guilabel:`Dodatne ure (kodirane)` se status "
"spremeni v :guilabel:`Odobreno` in polje :guilabel:`Dodatne ure` v zgornji "
"polovici obrazca se posodobi za prikaz odobrenih nadur."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:73
msgid ""
"Once partial overtime is approved, it is still possible to deny overtime by "
"clicking the :icon:`fa-times` icon next to the :guilabel:`Extra Hours` field "
"in the top half of the form, or clicking :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`Refuse` "
"at the end of the overtime entry in the *Overtime Details* tab."
msgstr ""
"Ko so delne nadure odobrene, je Ň°e vedno mogońće zavrniti nadure s klikom na "
"ikono :icon:`fa-times` poleg polja :guilabel:`Dodatne ure` v zgornji "
"polovici obrazca ali s klikom na :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`Zavrni` na "
"koncu vnosa nadur v zavihku *Podrobnosti nadur*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:79
msgid ""
"Occasionally, verifying an employee's location when checking-in may be "
"needed. The method the employee checked-in to work is found on the "
"individual record, in the :guilabel:`Mode` field."
msgstr ""
"Obńćasno je lahko potrebna overitev lokacije kadra pri prijavi. Nańćin, s "
"katerim se je kader prijavil na delo, je naveden v posameznem zapisu v "
"polju :guilabel:`Nańćin`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:82
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Mode` field is not modifiable, as it only logs the method the "
"attendance record was created."
msgstr ""
"Polja :guilabel:`Nańćin` ni mogońće spremeniti, saj se z njim zabeleŇĺi samo "
"metoda, s katero je bil ustvarjen zapis prisotnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:85
msgid "The possible options are:"
msgstr "MoŇĺne moŇĺnosti so:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:87
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Kiosk`: The employee physically checked in or out using "
"a :doc:`kiosk <kiosks>` device. The employee was present at the kiosk to "
"check-in."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kiosk`: Kader se je fizińćno prijavil ali odjavil z uporabo "
"naprave :doc:`kiosk <kiosks>`. Kader je bil prisoten pri kiosku ob prijavi."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Systray`: The employee checked in or out :doc:`directly from the "
"database <check_in_check_out>`. Depending on the :guilabel:`IP Address` "
"displayed on the detailed attendance record, the employee's location at the "
"time of check-in can be determined."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrstica sistema`: Kader se je prijavil ali "
"odjavil :doc:`neposredno iz baze podatkov <check_in_check_out>`. Glede "
"na :guilabel:`IP naslov`, prikazan na podrobnem zapisu prisotnosti, je "
"mogońće ugotoviti lokacijo kadra ob ńćasu prijave."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:92
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Manual`: The record was created manually in the **Attendances** "
"app. This is typically done by management, to add a missing record."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Rońćno`: Zapis je bil ustvarjen rońćno v aplikaciji "
"**Prisotnosti**. To obińćajno stori vodstvo, da doda manjkajońći zapis."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:96
msgid "Convert overtime to time off"
msgstr "Pretvarjanje nadur v odsotnost"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:98
msgid ""
"Some companies allow for the conversion of overtime into time off. To "
"convert all or a portion of overtime into time off, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Attendances app --> Management`. Click on the desired "
"attendance record to view the specific attendance details."
msgstr ""
"Nekatera podjetja omogońćajo pretvorbo nadur v odsotnost. Za pretvorbo vseh "
"ali dela nadur v odsotnost pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Prisotnosti "
"--> Upravljanje`. Kliknite na Ňĺeleni zapis prisotnosti za ogled dolońćenih "
"podrobnosti prisotnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:102
msgid ""
"In the *Overtime Details* tab, adjust the amount of overtime being converted "
"to time off in the :guilabel:`Extra Hours (encoded)` field, if necessary. "
"Next, click the checkbox in the :guilabel:`Compensable as Time Off` column, "
"indicating the overtime should be converted to time off. Click :icon:`fa-"
"check` :guilabel:`Approve` at the end of the line, and the status changes "
"to :guilabel:`Approved`, and the :guilabel:`Extra Hours` field in the top "
"half of the form updates to reflect the approved overtime."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku *Podrobnosti nadur* po potrebi prilagodite kolińćino nadur, ki se "
"pretvarjajo v odsotnost, v polju :guilabel:`Dodatne ure (kodirane)`. Nato "
"kliknite potrditveno polje v stolpcu :guilabel:`Nadomestljivo kot "
"odsotnost`, kar oznańćuje, da je treba nadure pretvoriti v odsotnost. "
"Kliknite :icon:`fa-check` :guilabel:`Odobri` na koncu vrstice in status se "
"spremeni v :guilabel:`Odobreno`, polje :guilabel:`Dodatne ure` v zgornji "
"polovici obrazca pa se posodobi, da odraŇĺa odobrene nadure."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:None
msgid "An attendance record with 2 ours of overtime converted to time off."
msgstr "Zapis prisotnosti z 2 urama nadur, pretvornjenimi v odsotnost."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:115
msgid "Create attendance records"
msgstr "Ustvarite evidence prisotnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:117
msgid ""
"When necessary, users with the required :ref:`access rights <employees/work-"
"info-tab>` are able to create attendance records manually in the "
"**Attendances** app. Some situations requiring this is when employees forget "
"to check in and out for shifts, as employees cannot retroactively create "
"attendance records."
msgstr ""
"Ko je potrebno, lahko uporabniki z zahtevanimi :ref:`pravicami dostopa "
"<employees/work-info-tab>` rońćno ustvarijo evidence prisotnosti v aplikaciji "
"**Prisotnosti**. Nekatere situacije, ki to zahtevajo, so, ko kader pozabi "
"prijaviti in odjaviti svoje izmene, saj kader ne more naknadno ustvariti "
"evidenc prisotnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:122
msgid ""
"To add a missing attendance record, navigate to :menuselection:`Attendances "
"app --> Overview --> Dashboard`. Click the :guilabel:`New` button in the "
"upper-left corner to open a *Create* pop-up window. Enter the following "
"information on the form, then click :guilabel:`Save & Close`:"
msgstr ""
"ńĆe Ňĺelite dodati manjkajońći zapis prisotnosti, se pomaknite "
"na :menuselection:`Aplikacija prisotnosti --> Pregled --> Nadzorna ploŇ°ńća`. "
"Kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Novo` v zgornjem levem kotu, da odprete pojavno "
"okno *Ustvari*. V obrazec vnesite naslednje podatke, nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani in zapri`:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:126
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Employee`: Select the employee the record is being created for. "
"The signed-in user populates this field, by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kader`: Izberite kadrovskega usluŇĺbenca, za katerega se ustvarja "
"zapis. To polje je privzeto izpolnjeno s prijavljenim uporabnikom."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:128
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Check In`: Using the calendar, select the check in date and time, "
"then click :guilabel:`Apply`. By default, the current date is selected, and "
"the time is set to `12:00:AM`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prijava`: S pomońćjo koledarja izberite datum in ńćas prijave, nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Uporabi`. Privzeto je izbran trenutni datum, ńćas pa je "
"nastavljen na `12:00:AM`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:130
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Check Out`: Using the calendar, select the check out date and "
"time, then click :guilabel:`Apply`. By default, the following date is "
"selected, and the time is set to `12:00:AM`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Odjava`: S pomońćjo koledarja izberite datum in ńćas odjave, nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Uporabi`. Privzeto je izbran naslednji datum, ńćas pa je "
"nastavljen na `12:00:AM`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:132
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Worked Time`: This field is automatically populated with the "
"difference from the selected :guilabel:`Check In` and :guilabel:`Check Out` "
"times. This field **cannot** be modified."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Delovni ńćas`: To polje se samodejno izpolni z razliko med "
"izbranima ńćasoma :guilabel:`Prijava` in :guilabel:`Odjava`. Tega polja **ni "
"mogońće** spremeniti."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Extra Hours`: This field is *not* modifiable as overtime must "
"be :ref:`approved <attendances/approve-refuse>`. This field displays zero "
"(`00:00`) by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dodatne ure`: Tega polja *ni mogońće* spremeniti, saj morajo biti "
"nadure :ref:`odobrene <attendances/approve-refuse>`. To polje privzeto "
"prikazuje nińć (`00:00`)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/management.rst:None
msgid ""
"An Attendances app record form, filled out for Mike Smith for January 27, "
"2026."
msgstr ""
"Izpolnjen obrazec zapisa v aplikaciji Prisotnosti za Mika Smitha za 27. "
"januar 2026."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:3
msgid "Overtime rulesets"
msgstr "Nabori pravil za nadure"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo's **Attendances** app allows for the configuration of overtime rules to "
"determine if and when employees earn overtime, and at what rate."
msgstr ""
"Odoo aplikacija **Prisotnost** omogońća konfiguracijo pravil za nadure, ki "
"dolońćajo, ali in kdaj zaposleni prisluŇĺijo nadure ter po kateri stopnji."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:9
msgid ""
"No overtime rulesets come preconfigured in the **Attendances** app; all "
"overtime rulesets must be created."
msgstr ""
"V aplikaciji **Prisotnost** ni prednastavljenih naborov pravil za nadure; "
"vse nabore pravil za nadure je treba ustvariti."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:13
msgid "Create an overtime ruleset"
msgstr "Ustvarite nabor pravil za nadure"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:15
msgid ""
"To create an overtime ruleset, navigate to :menuselection:`Attendances app --"
"> Configuration --> Overtime Rulesets`. Any existing overtime rulesets "
"appear in a default list view, and display the ruleset :guilabel:`Name`, "
"the :guilabel:`Rate Mode`, and the :guilabel:`Rules Count` (the number of "
"rules configured for the ruleset)."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje nabora pravil za nadure pojdite na :menuselection:`aplikacija "
"Prisotnost --> Konfiguracija --> Nabori pravil za nadure`. Vsi obstojeńći "
"nabori pravil za nadure se prikaŇĺejo v privzetem seznamskem pogledu in "
"prikazujejo :guilabel:`Ime` nabora pravil, :guilabel:`Nańćin stopnje` "
"in :guilabel:`Ň†tevilo pravil` (Ň°tevilo pravil, konfiguriranih za nabor "
"pravil)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:20
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`New` button, and a blank :guilabel:`Rulesets` form "
"loads. Enter the following information on the top half of the form:"
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Novo` in naloŇĺi se prazen obrazec :guilabel:`Nabori "
"pravil`. V zgornjo polovico obrazca vnesite naslednje informacije:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:23
msgid ":guilabel:`Ruleset Name`: Enter a name for the ruleset."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ime nabora pravil`: Vnesite ime za nabor pravil."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:24
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Rate Combination Mode`: Using the drop-down menu, select how the "
"overtime rate is calculated. The options are:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nańćin kombinacije stopnje`: V spustnem meniju izberite, kako se "
"izrańćuna stopnja nadur. MoŇĺnosti so:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:27
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Maximum Rate`: The highest rate is used to determine the overtime "
"pay. For example, if there are two available rates of 150% and 125%, the "
"highest available rate, 150%, is applied."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`NajviŇ°ja stopnja`: Za dolońćitev plańćila nadur se uporabi najviŇ°ja "
"stopnja. Na primer, ńće sta na voljo dve stopnji, 150 % in 125 %, se uporabi "
"najviŇ°ja razpoloŇĺljiva stopnja, 150 %."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sum of all rates`: A combination of all applicable overtime rates "
"is used to calculate the overtime pay. Odoo calculates the rate by adding "
"the *extra* pay rates (above 100%)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vsota vseh stopenj`: Za izrańćun plańćila nadur se uporabi "
"kombinacija vseh veljavnih stopenj nadur. Odoo izrańćuna stopnjo tako, da "
"seŇ°teje *dodatne* plańćilne stopnje (nad 100 %)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:34
msgid ""
"Two overtime rates are cteated, one for 150% and the other for 120%. "
"The :guilabel:`Sum of all rates` option is selected. The overtime rate "
"applied is 170%."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjeni sta dve stopnji nadur, ena za 150 % in druga za 120 %. Izbrana je "
"moŇĺnost :guilabel:`Vsota vseh stopenj`. Uporabljena stopnja nadur je 170 %."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:37
msgid ""
"The calculation used to determine this rate is: 100% (baseline) + (150-100)% "
"+ (120-100)% = 170%."
msgstr ""
"Izrańćun, uporabljen za dolońćitev te stopnje, je: 100 % (osnova) + (150-100) "
"% + (120-100) % = 170 %."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:40
msgid ":guilabel:`Description`: Enter a brief description for the ruleset."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Opis`: Vnesite kratek opis nabora pravil."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:41
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Country`: Using the drop-down menu, select the country the "
"ruleset applies to."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`DrŇĺava`: V spustnem meniju izberite drŇĺavo, za katero velja nabor "
"pravil."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:44
msgid "Overtime rules"
msgstr "Pravila za nadure"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:46
msgid ""
"Once the main information of the ruleset is created, the next step is to add "
"the individual rules. Click :guilabel:`Add a line` at the bottom of the "
"*Overtime Rules* tab of the :guilabel:`Ruleset` form, and a *Create Rule* "
"pop-up window loads."
msgstr ""
"Ko so ustvarjene glavne informacije nabora pravil, je naslednji korak "
"dodajanje posameznih pravil. Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico` na dnu "
"zavihka *Pravila za nadure* obrazca :guilabel:`Nabor pravil` in naloŇĺi se "
"pojavno okno *Ustvari pravilo*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:50
msgid ""
"Enter the :guilabel:`Rule Name` in the corresponding field. Next, enter the "
"following information in the *Definition* tab:"
msgstr ""
"V ustrezno polje vnesite :guilabel:`Ime pravila`. Nato vnesite naslednje "
"informacije v zavihek *Definicija*:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:54
msgid "Condition section"
msgstr "Razdelek pogoj"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:56
msgid ""
"This section determines what logged time counts as overtime. Rules can be "
"based on :ref:`quantity <attendnaces/quantity>` or :ref:`timing <attendnaces/"
"timing>`."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek dolońća, kateri prijavljeni ńćas Ň°teje kot nadurno delo. Pravila "
"so lahko osnovana na :ref:`kolińćini <attendnaces/quantity>` ali :ref:`ńćasu "
"<attendnaces/timing>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:62
msgid "Based on quantity"
msgstr "Glede na kolińćino"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:64
msgid ""
"If overtime is accrued when the total logged hours for a day or week exceed "
"what is expected, select the :guilabel:`Quantity` radio button for "
"the :guilabel:`The rule is based on` field. Configure the rest of the fields "
"in the *Condition* section as follows:"
msgstr ""
"ńĆe se nadureobeńćujejo, ko skupno prijavljene ure za dan ali teden presegajo "
"prińćakovano, izberite radijski gumb :guilabel:`Kolińćina` za "
"polje :guilabel:`Pravilo temelji na`. Preostala polja v razdelku *Pogoj* "
"konfigurirajte na naslednji nańćin:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:68
msgid ""
":guilabel:`If the worked hours on a (Day/Week) differs`: First, select if "
"the total expected time is calculated by the :guilabel:`Day` "
"or :guilabel:`Week`, using the drop-down menu. Next, select if the "
"difference is compared:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ńĆe se delovna ura v (dnevu/tednu) razlikuje`: Najprej izberite, "
"ali se skupni prińćakovani ńćas izrańćuna po :guilabel:`Dnevu` "
"ali :guilabel:`Tednu` z uporabo spustnega menija. Nato izberite, ali se "
"razlika primerja:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:72
msgid ""
":guilabel:`from the amount defined on the contract`: Select this option if "
"the overtime is based on the working hours :ref:`defined on the employees "
"contract <payroll/gen-info>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`od zneska, dolońćenega v pogodbi`: Izberite to moŇĺnost, ńće nadure "
"temeljijo na delovnem ńćasu :ref:`dolońćenem v pogodbi zaposlenega <payroll/"
"gen-info>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:74
msgid ""
":guilabel:`from a specific duration`: Select this option if the overtime is "
"based on a specified amount of time. If this is selected, "
"a :guilabel:`Duration to exceed` field appears. Enter the number "
"of :guilabel:`hours` in an `HH:MM` format the employee must exceed "
"each :guilabel:`Day` or :guilabel:`Week`, depending on what is selected in "
"the :guilabel:`If the worked hours on a (Day/Week) differs` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`od dolońćenega trajanja`: Izberite to moŇĺnost, ńće nadure temeljijo "
"na dolońćenem ńćasovnem znesku. ńĆe je to izbrano, se prikazuje "
"polje :guilabel:`Trajanje za prekorańćitev`. Vnesite Ň°tevilo :guilabel:`ur` v "
"formatu `HH:MM`, ki jih mora zaposleni preseńći vsak :guilabel:`Dan` "
"ali :guilabel:`Teden`, odvisno od tega, kaj je izbrano v polju :guilabel:`ńĆe "
"se delovna ura v (dnevu/tednu) razlikuje`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:80
msgid ""
":guilabel:`With a tolerance in favor of the employer of`: This field defines "
"a buffer of time that is *not* considered overtime. Enter the amount in a "
"`HH:MM` format. For example, if this field is set to `00:15`, and an "
"employee logs an 8 hour and 13 minute workday, the extra 13 minutes is "
"**not** counted as overtime."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`S toleranco v prid delodajalca`: To polje dolońća varnostni ńćas, "
"ki se *ne* Ň°teje kot nadure. Vnesite znesek v formatu `HH:MM`. Na primer, ńće "
"je to polje nastavljeno na `00:15` in zaposleni prijavi 8 ur in 13 minut "
"delovnega dne, dodatnih 13 minut **ni** Ň°tetih kot nadure."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:84
msgid ""
":guilabel:`With a tolerance in favor of the employee of`: Enter the amount "
"of extra time given to an employee as overtime, in a `HH:MM` format. For "
"example, if this field is set to `00:15`, and an employee logs an 8 hour and "
"48 minute workday, the missing 12 minutes **are** counted as overtime, for a "
"total of one full hour of overtime (instead of only 48 minutes of overtime)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`S toleranco v prid zaposlenega`: Vnesite kolińćino dodatnega ńćasa, "
"dodeljeno zaposlenemu kot nadure, v formatu `HH:MM`. Na primer, ńće je to "
"polje nastavljeno na `00:15` in zaposleni prijavi 8 ur in 48 minut delovnega "
"dne, manjkajońćih 12 minut **je** Ň°tetih kot nadure, kar znese skupno eno "
"polno uro nadur (namesto samo 48 minut nadur)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:92
msgid "Based on timing"
msgstr "Glede na ńćas"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:94
msgid ""
"If overtime is accrued only on specific days or at specific times, select "
"the :guilabel:`Timing` radio button for the :guilabel:`The rule is based on` "
"field. Configure the rest of the fields in the *Condition* section as "
"follows:"
msgstr ""
"ńĆe se nadure obrańćunavajo samo na dolońćene dneve ali ob dolońćenih ńćasih, "
"izberite radijski gumb :guilabel:`ńĆas` za polje :guilabel:`Pravilo temelji "
"na`. Preostala polja v razdelku *Pogoj* konfigurirajte na naslednji nańćin:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:98
msgid ""
":guilabel:`With a tolerance in favor of the employer of`: This field defines "
"a buffer of time that is *not* considered overtime. Enter the amount in a "
"`HH:MM` format. For example, if this field is set to `00:15`, and an "
"employee logs a 40 hour and 13 minute workweek, the extra 13 minutes is "
"**not** counted as overtime."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`S toleranco v prid delodajalca`: To polje dolońća varnostni ńćas, "
"ki se *ne* Ň°teje kot nadure. Vnesite znesek v formatu `HH:MM`. Na primer, ńće "
"je to polje nastavljeno na `00:15` in zaposleni prijavi 40 ur in 13 minut "
"delovnega tedna, dodatnih 13 minut **ni** Ň°tetih kot nadure."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:102
msgid ""
":guilabel:`With a tolerance in favor of the employee of`: Enter the amount "
"of extra time given to an employee as overtime, in a `HH:MM` format. For "
"example, if this field is set to `00:15`, and an employee logs a 40 hour and "
"48 minute workweek, the missing 12 minutes **is** counted as overtime, for a "
"total of one full hour of overtime (instead of only 48 minutes of overtime)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`S toleranco v prid zaposlenega`: Vnesite kolińćino dodatnega ńćasa, "
"dodeljeno zaposlenemu kot nadure, v formatu `HH:MM`. Na primer, ńće je to "
"polje nastavljeno na `00:15` in zaposleni prijavi 40 ur in 48 minut "
"delovnega tedna, manjkajońćih 12 minut **je** Ň°tetih kot nadure, kar znese "
"skupno eno polno uro nadur (namesto samo 48 minut nadur)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:106
msgid ""
":guilabel:`If the employee works`: Click the radio button to select the "
"period of time defined for accruing overtime. The options are:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ńĆe zaposleni dela`: Kliknite radijski gumb za izbiro ńćasovnega "
"obdobja, dolońćenega za obrańćunavanje nadur. MoŇĺnosti so:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:109
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On any working day`: Select this option if overtime is accrued if "
"an employee works outside of a specified set of hours for any working day. "
"When selected, a :guilabel:`Between` field appears, listing `00:00` and "
"`24:00` hours, by default. Adjust the working times in an `HH:MM` for both "
"fields, defining the specific working hours an employee earns overtime for."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Na katerikoli delovni dan`: Izberite to moŇĺnost, ńće se nadure "
"obrańćunavajo, ńće zaposleni dela zunaj dolońćenega sklopa ur za katerikoli "
"delovni dan. Ko je izbrano, se prikazuje polje :guilabel:`Med`, ki privzeto "
"navaja `00:00` in `24:00` ur. Prilagodite delovne ńćase v formatu `HH:MM` za "
"obe polji, da dolońćite specifińćne delovne ure, za katere zaposleni zasluŇĺi "
"nadure."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:115
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Between` hours are set to `09:00` and `17:00`. An employee "
"works from 7:00 AM until 4:00 PM. The employee earns 2 hours of overtime, "
"for the hours between 7:00 AM and 9:00 AM."
msgstr ""
"Ure :guilabel:`Med` so nastavljene na `09:00` in `17:00`. Zaposleni dela od "
"7:00 do 16:00. Zaposleni zasluŇĺi 2 uri nadur za ure med 7:00 in 9:00."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:119
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On any non-working day`: Select this option if overtime is "
"accrued if an employee works outside of a specified set of hours for any non-"
"working day. When selected, a :guilabel:`Between` field appears, listing "
"`00:00` and `24:00` hours, by default. Adjust the working times in an "
"`HH:MM` for both fields, defining the specific working hours an employee "
"earns overtime for."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Na katerikoli nedelovni dan`: Izberite to moŇĺnost, ńće se nadure "
"obrańćunavajo, ńće zaposleni dela zunaj dolońćenega sklopa ur za katerikoli "
"nedelovni dan. Ko je izbrano, se prikazuje polje :guilabel:`Med`, ki "
"privzeto navaja `00:00` in `24:00` ur. Prilagodite delovne ńćase v formatu "
"`HH:MM` za obe polji, da dolońćite specifińćne delovne ure, za katere "
"zaposleni zasluŇĺi nadure."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:124
msgid ""
":guilabel:`When employee is off`: Select this option if overtime is accrued "
"on any day the employee is *not* scheduled to work."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ko je zaposleni odsoten`: Izberite to moŇĺnost, ńće se nadure "
"obrańćunavajo na katerikoli dan, ko zaposleni *ni* na razporedu za delo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:126
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Outside of a specific schedule`: Select this option if overtime "
"is accrued when employees work outside of a selected :doc:`working schedule "
"<../payroll/working_schedules>`. When selected, a :guilabel:`Schedule` field "
"appears. Using the drop-down menu, select the working schedule used to "
"determine overtime."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zunaj specifińćnega urnika`: Izberite to moŇĺnost, ńće se nadure "
"obrańćunavajo, ko zaposleni delajo zunaj izbranega :doc:`delovnega urnika <../"
"payroll/working_schedules>`. Ko je izbrano, se prikazuje "
"polje :guilabel:`Urnik`. Z uporabo spustnega menija izberite delovni urnik, "
"uporabljen za dolońćanje nadur."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:132
msgid "Action section"
msgstr "Razdelek dejanje"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:134
msgid ""
"Once the criteria set in the *Condition* section are met, the *Action* "
"section determines how any approved extra time is handled."
msgstr ""
"Ko so izpolnjena merila, dolońćena v razdelku *Pogoj*, razdelek *Dejanje* "
"dolońća, kako se obravnava odobreni dodatni ńćas."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:137
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pay extra hours`: Enable this checkbox if overtime hours are paid "
"out. If enabled, a percentage field appears to the right of the checkmark, "
"populated with the rate defined on the overtime :ref:`work entry type "
"<payroll/work-entry-types>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Plańćaj dodatne ure`: Omogońćite to potrditveno polje, ńće se "
"nadurne ure izplańćajo. ńĆe je omogońćeno, se desno od kljukice prikaŇĺe polje "
"za odstotek, izpolnjeno s stopnjo, dolońćeno pri :ref:`vrsti vnosa dela "
"<payroll/work-entry-types>` za nadurno delo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:140
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Work entry type to use`: This field only appears if "
"the :guilabel:`Pay extra hours` field is enabled. Using the drop-down menu, "
"select what :ref:`work entry type <payroll/work-entry-types>` is created for "
"the overtime. By default, :guilabel:`Overtime Hours` is selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta vnosa dela za uporabo`: To polje se prikaŇĺe samo, ńće je "
"omogońćeno polje :guilabel:`Plańćaj dodatne ure`. V spustnem meniju izberite, "
"katera :ref:`vrsta vnosa dela <payroll/work-entry-types>` se ustvari za "
"nadurno delo. Privzeto je izbrano :guilabel:`Nadurne ure`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:144
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Give back as time off`: Enable this checkbox if the overtime "
"should be converted to time off, instead of being paid out."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrni kot odsotnost`: Omogońćite to potrditveno polje, ńće naj se "
"nadurno delo pretvori v odsotnost namesto v izplańćilo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:148
msgid "Example overtime ruleset"
msgstr "Primer niza pravil za nadurno delo"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:150
msgid ""
"A United States-based company wants to grant time and a half overtime to all "
"employees who work more than their 40-hour work week, or work on any non-"
"working day. To configure this, they create a ruleset called `Overtime`, "
"with a :guilabel:`Rate Combination Mode` set to :guilabel:`Maximum Rate`. "
"The country is set to :guilabel:`United States`, and "
"a :guilabel:`Description` is entered explaining the overtime rules."
msgstr ""
"AmeriŇ°ko podjetje Ňĺeli vsem zaposlenim, ki delajo veńć kot 40-urni delovni "
"teden ali delajo na katerikoli dela prost dan, dodeliti nadurno delo po "
"stopnji ena in pol. Za to konfiguracijo ustvarijo niz pravil z imenom "
"`Overtime`, pri ńćemer je :guilabel:`Nańćin kombinacije stopnje` nastavljen "
"na :guilabel:`Najveńćja stopnja`. DrŇĺava je nastavljena "
"na :guilabel:`ZdruŇĺene drŇĺave` in vnesen je :guilabel:`Opis`, ki pojasnjuje "
"pravila za nadurno delo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:None
msgid "The top half of the overtime ruleset for the example."
msgstr "Zgornja polovica niza pravil za nadurno delo za primer."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:159
msgid ""
"Two rules are configured in the *Overtime Rules* tab: :ref:`Employee "
"Schedule Rule <attendnaces/schedule-rule>` and :ref:`Non Working Days Rule "
"<attendnaces/hours-rule>`."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku *Pravila za nadurno delo* sta konfigurirani dve "
"pravili: :ref:`Pravilo urnika zaposlenega <attendnaces/schedule-rule>` "
"in :ref:`Pravilo za dela proste dni <attendnaces/hours-rule>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:165
msgid "Employee schedule rule"
msgstr "Pravilo urnika zaposlenega"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:167
msgid ""
"The *Employee Schedule Rule* is based on :guilabel:`Quantity`, and employees "
"accrue overtime if they work more than the :guilabel:`amount defined on the "
"contract` on any given :guilabel:`Day`. No tolerance set for either the "
"employee or the employer. If the employee works overtime, they are paid at a "
"rate of :guilabel:`150%`, and the time is logged as :guilabel:`Overtime "
"Hours` on their attendance log."
msgstr ""
"*Pravilo urnika zaposlenega* temelji na :guilabel:`Kolińćini` in zaposleni "
"pridobijo nadurno delo, ńće delajo veńć kot :guilabel:`kolińćina, dolońćena v "
"pogodbi`, v kateremkoli :guilabel:`Dnevu`. Ni dolońćene tolerance ne za "
"zaposlenega ne za delodajalca. ńĆe zaposleni dela nadurno, se mu plańća po "
"stopnji :guilabel:`150 %` in ńćas se zabeleŇĺi kot :guilabel:`Nadurne ure` v "
"dnevniku prisotnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:None
msgid ""
"The rule set for an employee who works more than their scheduled work day."
msgstr ""
"Pravilo, dolońćeno za zaposlenega, ki dela veńć kot njegov predvideni delovni "
"dan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:179
msgid "Non-working days rule"
msgstr "Pravilo za dela proste dni"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/overtime.rst:181
msgid ""
"The *Non-Working Days Rule* is based on :guilabel:`Timing`, and employees "
"accrue overtime if they work :guilabel:`on any non-working day`, regardless "
"of the time. No tolerance is set for either the employee or the employer. If "
"the employee works overtime, they are paid at a rate of :guilabel:`150%`, "
"and the time is logged as :guilabel:`Overtime Hours` on their attendance log."
msgstr ""
"*Pravilo za dela proste dni* temelji na :guilabel:`ńĆasovnem razporedu` in "
"zaposleni pridobijo nadurno delo, ńće delajo :guilabel:`na katerikoli dela "
"prost dan`, ne glede na ńćas. Ni dolońćene tolerance ne za zaposlenega ne za "
"delodajalca. ńĆe zaposleni dela nadurno, se mu plańća po "
"stopnji :guilabel:`150 %` in ńćas se zabeleŇĺi kot :guilabel:`Nadurne ure` v "
"dnevniku prisotnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/employees.rst:5
#: ../../content/applications/hr/employees.rst:81
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:91
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:67
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:86
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:69
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:58
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:35
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:97
msgid "Employees"
msgstr "Kadri"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/employees.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo **Employees** centralizes :doc:`personnel files <employees/"
"new_employee>`, employment :doc:`contracts <payroll/contracts>`, "
"and :doc:`departmental hierarchies <employees/departments>` in one system. "
"In addition, each employee record tracks :doc:`certifications <employees/"
"certifications>` and :doc:`training <employees/learning>`, "
"earned :doc:`badges <employees/badges>`, and all assigned :doc:`equipment "
"<employees/equipment>`. Customizable :doc:`onboarding <employees/"
"onboarding>` and :doc:`offboarding <employees/offboarding>` programs ensure "
"all employees are trained and ready for work, and all required steps are "
"taken when they leave."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Kader** centralizira :doc:`osebne mape <employees/"
"new_employee>`, :doc:`pogodbe <payroll/contracts>` o zaposlitvi "
"in :doc:`oddelńćne hierarhije <employees/departments>` v enem sistemu. Poleg "
"tega vsak zapis o zaposlenem spremlja :doc:`certifikate <employees/"
"certifications>` in :doc:`usposabljanja <employees/learning>`, "
"pridobljene :doc:`znańćke <employees/badges>` in vso dodeljeno :doc:`opremo "
"<employees/equipment>`. Prilagodljivi programi :doc:`uvajanja <employees/"
