msgstr ""
"ńĆe je omejitev :guilabel:`Zahteva za novo vozilo` nastavljena na 20 vozil in "
"je na voljo 25 vozil, zaposleni ne morejo zahtevati novega avtomobila in "
"morajo izbrati med Ňĺe razpoloŇĺljivimi 25 vozili. ńĆe je na voljo samo 10 "
"avtomobilov, bi lahko zaposleni zahteval novo vozilo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/fleet/new_vehicle.rst:79
msgid ""
"This settings option **only** appears if the :guilabel:`Belgian-Payroll-"
"Fleet` module is installed for the Belgian localization."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitvena moŇĺnost se prikaŇĺe **samo**, ńće je za belgijsko lokalizacijo "
"nameŇ°ńćen modul :guilabel:`Belgian-Payroll-Fleet`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/fleet/new_vehicle.rst:83
msgid "Add a vehicle"
msgstr "Dodajanje vozila"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/fleet/new_vehicle.rst:85
msgid ""
"To add a new vehicle to the fleet from the :guilabel:`Vehicles` dashboard, "
"click the :guilabel:`New` button in the top-left corner, and a blank vehicle "
