":guilabel:`Model`: V spustnem meniju izberite model vozila. Ko je model "
"izbran, se lahko na obrazcu pojavijo dodatna polja. ńĆe model ni naveden, "
"vnesite ime modela in kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari \"model\"` "
"ali :guilabel:`Ustvari in uredi...`, da :ref:`ustvarite nov model in uredite "
"podrobnosti modela <fleet/add-model>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/fleet/new_vehicle.rst:98
msgid ":guilabel:`License Plate`: Enter the vehicle's license plate number."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Registrska tablica`: Vnesite registrsko Ň°tevilko vozila."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/fleet/new_vehicle.rst:99
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tags`: Select any tags from the drop-down menu, or type in a new "
"tag. There is no limit on the amount of tags that can be selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Znańćke`: Izberite poljubne znańćke iz spustnega menija ali vnesite "
"novo znańćko. Ň†tevilo izbranih znańćk ni omejeno."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/fleet/new_vehicle.rst:None
msgid "The new vehicle form, showing the model section."
msgstr "Obrazec za novo vozilo z razdelkom za model."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/fleet/new_vehicle.rst:106
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Model` is the *only* required field on the new vehicle form. "
