"**Kader**, se Ň°tevilka mobilnostne kartice samodejno prikaŇĺe v tem polju. ńĆe "
"mobilnostna kartica ni navedena in bi jo bilo treba dodati, :ref:`uredite "
"kadrovski zapis <employees/hr-settings>` v aplikaciji **Kader**."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/fleet/new_vehicle.rst:131
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Future Driver`: If the next driver for the vehicle is known, "
"select the next driver from the drop-down menu. Or, type in the next driver "
