"posodobljeni, se posodobi tudi polje :guilabel:`Plańća`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:109
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contract Type`: Using the drop-down menu, select one of the 18 "
"default types of contracts. This list is the same as the *employment type*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta pogodbe`: Iz spustnega menija izberite eno od 18 privzetih "
