"praksa je, da preverite ta tri polja, ńće so bile izvedene kakrŇ°nekoli "
"spremembe, da zagotovite njihovo natanńćnost."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:143
msgid ":guilabel:`Wage on Signature`: Enter the monthly wage in the field."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Plańća ob podpisu`: Vnesite meseńćno plańćo v polje."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/contracts.rst:146
