msgstr ""
"Oprostitev se uporablja samo za del delovnega ńćasa, namenjenega znanstvenemu "
"raziskovanju, ki zajema temeljne raziskave, industrijske raziskave ali "
"eksperimentalni razvoj."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:2986
msgid "This exemption does not affect the net salary of employees."
msgstr "Ta oprostitev ne vpliva na neto plańćo zaposlenih."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:2989
msgid "Capping rules"
msgstr "Pravila o omejitvah"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:2991
msgid ""
"The total exemption granted to researchers with a bachelor's degree is "
"limited to 25% of the exemption granted to PhD and master's degree holders. "
"For small companies (as defined in Article 15 ¬ß¬ß 1-6 of the Companies Code), "
"this limit is doubled. These rules have remained unchanged since January 1, "
"2020."
msgstr ""
"Skupna oprostitev, dodeljena raziskovalcem z visokoŇ°olsko diplomo, je "
"omejena na 25 % oprostitve, dodeljene imetnicam in imetnikom doktorata ter "
"magistrske diplome. Za mala podjetja (kot so opredeljena v ńćlenu 15 ¬ß¬ß 1-6 "
"Zakonika o druŇĺbah) je ta omejitev podvojena. Ta pravila so ostala "
"nespremenjena od 1. januarja 2020."

