"paketne postavke knjiŇĺenja v konfiguraciji plańćnih list za serije izplańćil). "
"Kliknite gumb :guilabel:`KnjiŇĺi`. Vse plańćilne liste se samodejno "
"konsolidirajo kot en vnos v dnevnik."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:575
msgid "Register payment"
msgstr "Registriraj plańćilo"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:577
msgid ""
"After the journal entries are validated, Odoo generates payment report files."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vnosi v dnevnik potrjeni, Odoo ustvari datoteke s porońćili o plańćilih."

