#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:276
msgid ""
"Tax brackets are applied progressively. This means each portion of an "
"employee's income is taxed at its respective rate within each bracket, "
"rather than their entire income being taxed at the highest rate they fall "
"into."
msgstr ""
"Davńćne stopnje se uporabljajo progresivno. To pomeni, da se vsak del dohodka "
"kadra obdavńći po ustrezni stopnji znotraj vsakega razreda, namesto da bi bil "
"celoten dohodek obdavńćen po najviŇ°ji stopnji, v katero spada."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:281
msgid ""
"Turkish employees benefit from a monthly personal income tax **exemption**, "
"which is adjusted each year. For 2025, the exemption amount is TRY 3,315.70 "
"per month, from January through July."
msgstr ""
"TurŇ°ki kader ima pravico do meseńćne oprostitve dohodnine, ki se vsako leto "
"prilagodi. Za leto 2025 znaŇ°a oprostitev TRY 3.315,70 meseńćno, od januarja "
"do julija."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:285
msgid "Stamp Tax"
msgstr "Kolkovina"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:287
msgid ""
"Stamp tax is applied to gross salary payments in T√ľrkiye. The standard rate "
"is 0.759% (i.e. 7.59 per thousand), which is withheld from the employee's "
"gross wage and remitted to the tax authority :abbr:`GIB (Gelir ńįdaresi "
"BaŇükanlińüi,)` by the employer."
msgstr ""
"Kolkovina se v Turńćiji uporablja za bruto plańćo. Standardna stopnja je 0,759 "
"% (tj. 7,59 na tisońć), ki se odtegne od bruto plańće kadra in jo delodajalec "
"nakaŇĺe davńćnemu organu :abbr:`GIB (Gelir ńįdaresi BaŇükanlńĪńüńĪ)`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:291
msgid ""
"The base amount for the stamp tax is the total gross salary amount "
"(including bonuses or extras)."
msgstr ""
"Osnova za kolkovino je skupna bruto plańća (vkljuńćno s premijami ali dodatki)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:294
msgid ""
"Turkish employees receive a personal stamp tax **exemption**, the value of "
"which is updated annually. As of 2025, the exemption amount is TRY 197.38 "
"per month, from January through July. This applies to gross earnings up to "
"the legal minimum wage level before calculating stamp tax."
msgstr ""
"TurŇ°ki kader prejme osebno oprostitev kolkovine, katere vrednost se letno "
"posodobi. Od leta 2025 znaŇ°a oprostitev TRY 197,38 meseńćno, od januarja do "
"julija. To velja za bruto zasluŇĺek do viŇ°ine zakonske minimalne plańće pred "
"izrańćunom kolkovine."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:299
msgid "Net to gross"
msgstr "Neto v bruto"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:301
msgid ""
"On an employee record, if the option :guilabel:`Net to Gross` is enabled in "
"the :ref:`contract section <payroll/turkey_contract>` of the payroll tab, "
"the net salary is fixed, and specified in the :guilabel:`Net Wage` field, "
"while the gross wage is recalculated each month, and increases throughout "
"the year."
msgstr ""
"V zapisu kadra, ńće je moŇĺnost :guilabel:`Neto v bruto` omogońćena "
"v :ref:`razdelku pogodbe <payroll/turkey_contract>` zavihka plańćnih "
"seznamov, je neto plańća fiksna in dolońćena v polju :guilabel:`Neto plańća`, "
"medtem ko se bruto plańća prerańćunava vsak mesec in se skozi leto poveńća."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:306
msgid ""
"The gross wage is what tax calculations are based on, so for these "
"employees, the monthly *net* wage does **not** change, but the monthly "
"*gross* amount is recalculated each month, changing the taxes with it."
msgstr ""
"Bruto plańća je osnova za izrańćun davkov, zato se pri tem kadru meseńćna "
"*neto* plańća **ne** spremeni, ampak se meseńćni *bruto* znesek prerańćunava "
"vsak mesec, s ńćimer se spremenijo tudi davki."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:310
msgid ""
"In this scenario, the least amount of taxes are paid in the beginning of the "
"year, and taxes increase as the year progresses."
msgstr ""
"V tem scenariju se najmanj davkov plańća na zańćetku leta, davki pa se "
"poveńćujejo z napredovanjem leta."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:314
msgid ""
"On January 31st, an employee's year-to-date total income is ‚āļ10,000. The "
"income tax is calculated based on the ‚āļ10,000, which in this example is "
"‚āļ800. In February, the employee's year-to-date gross is ‚āļ20,000, and the "
"taxes are calculated based on that figure, for a total of ‚āļ2,000."
msgstr ""
"31. januarja znaŇ°a letni skupni dohodek kadra 10.000 TRY. Dohodnina se "
"izrańćuna na podlagi 10.000 TRY, kar je v tem primeru 800 TRY. V februarju "
"znaŇ°a letni bruto dohodek kadra 20.000 TRY in davki so izrańćunani na podlagi "
"te Ň°tevilke, skupaj 2.000 TRY."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:318
msgid ""
"Since the employee already paid ‚āļ800 in January, the taxes due for February "
"are ‚āļ1,200 because the employee already paid ‚āļ800 toward that total (‚āļ2,000 "
"- ‚āļ800 = ‚āļ1,200)."
msgstr ""
"Ker je kader Ňĺe plańćal 800 TRY v januarju, znaŇ°ajo davki za februar 1.200 "
"TRY, ker je kader Ňĺe plańćal 800 TRY tega skupnega zneska (2.000 TRY - 800 "
"TRY = 1.200 TRY)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:322
msgid "Gross to net"
msgstr "Bruto v neto"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:324
msgid ""
"On an employee record, if the option :guilabel:`Net to Gross` is **not** "
"enabled in the :ref:`contract section <payroll/turkey_contract>` of the "
"payroll tab, the gross salary is calculated based on the :guilabel:`Wage` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"V zapisu kadra, ńće moŇĺnost :guilabel:`Neto v bruto` **ni** omogońćena "
"v :ref:`razdelku pogodbe <payroll/turkey_contract>` zavihka plańćnih "
"seznamov, se bruto plańća izrańćuna na podlagi polja :guilabel:`Plańća`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:328
msgid ""
"The gross wage then has all the salary rules computed, to determine the "
"*net* wage. The taxes are then computed based on the gross wage. In this "
"scenario, unlike with net to gross, taxes are more consistent and do not "
"change that much, from month to month."
msgstr ""
"Bruto plańća nato vkljuńćuje vsa pravila o plańćah, da se dolońći *neto* plańća. "
"Davki se nato izrańćunajo na podlagi bruto plańće. V tem scenariju, za razliko "
"od neto v bruto, so davki bolj dosledni in se ne spreminjajo veliko iz "
"meseca v mesec."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:333
msgid ""
"The gross from net calculation depends on the salary rules defined in "
"the :guilabel:`T√ľrkiye: Monthly Pay` salary structure. Changes made to those "
"rules affect the computed amount."
msgstr ""
"Izrańćun bruto iz neto je odvisen od pravil o plańćah, dolońćenih v strukturi "
"plańć :guilabel:`Turńćija: meseńćna plańća`. Spremembe teh pravil vplivajo na "
"izrańćunani znesek."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:337
msgid "Run T√ľrkiye payroll"
msgstr "Izvajanje turŇ°kih plańćnih seznamov"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:382
msgid ""
"The accounting process when running payroll has two "
"components: :ref:`creating journal entries <payroll/journal-tr>` "
"and :ref:`registering payments <payroll/register-tr>`."
msgstr ""
"Rańćunovodski postopek pri izvajanju plańćnih seznamov ima dve "
"komponenti: :ref:`ustvarjanje dnevniŇ°kih vnosov <payroll/journal-tr>` "
"in :ref:`registracija plańćil <payroll/register-tr>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:405
msgid ""
"After the :ref:`journal entries <payroll/journal-tr>` are validated, Odoo "
"can generate payments."
msgstr ""
"Po preverjanju :ref:`kontnih vknjiŇĺb <payroll/journal-tr>` lahko Odoo "
"ustvari plańćila."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:408
msgid ""
"To generate payments from payslips, employees **must** have a *trusted* bank "
"account. If the employee's bank account is *not* marked as `trusted`, "
"payments **cannot** be generated through Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje plańćil iz obrańćunskih listov **morajo** imeti kadri *zaupni* "
"banńćni rańćun. ńĆe banńćni rańćun kadra *ni* oznańćen kot `zaupni`, plańćil **ni "
"mogońće** ustvariti prek Odooja."

