"je moŇĺnost :guilabel:`Standardnih 40 ur/teden`. ńĆe se potrebni delovni ńćas "
"ne pojavi na seznamu, :ref:`je mogońće ustvariti nov niz privzetega delovnega "
"ńćasa <payroll/new-default-working-hours>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:85
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Regular Pay Structure`: Type in the name for the regular pay "
"structure. It is used as the default option when generating payslips."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Redna plańćna struktura`: Vnesite ime za redno plańćno strukturo. "
"Uporablja se kot privzeta moŇĺnost pri ustvarjanju plańćilnih listov."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:87
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default Work Entry Type`: Select the default work entry type "
"which is used to create all work entries for the employee."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Privzeta vrsta delovnega vnosa`: Izberite privzeto vrsto "
"delovnega vnosa, ki se uporablja za ustvarjanje vseh delovnih vnosov za "
"zaposlenega."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:None
msgid "New structure type form to fill out when creating a new structure type."
msgstr ""
"Obrazec za nov tip strukture, ki ga je treba izpolniti pri ustvarjanju "
"novega tipa strukture."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:96
msgid "New default working hours"
msgstr "Nove privzete delovne ure"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:98
msgid ""
"To make new default working hours, type the name for the new working hours "
"in the :guilabel:`Default Working Hours` field on the new structure type "
"form. Click :guilabel:`Create and edit`. A default working hours form pops "
"up. The default working hours form has two sections: a general information "
"section, and a tab listing all the individual working hours by day and time. "
"When the form is completed, click :guilabel:`Save & Close`."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje novega privzetega delovnega ńćasa vnesite ime za nov delovni "
"ńćas v polje :guilabel:`Privzeti delovni ńćas` na obrazcu nove vrste "
"strukture. Kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari in uredi`. PrikaŇĺe se obrazec za "
"privzeti delovni ńćas. Obrazec za privzeti delovni ńćas ima dva razdelka: "
"razdelek s sploŇ°nimi informacijami in zavihek z navedbo vseh posameznih "
"delovnih ur po dnevu in ńćasu. Ko je obrazec izpolnjen, "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani in zapri`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:104
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Name`: Type in the name for the new default working hours. This "
"should be descriptive and clear to understand, such as `Standard 20 Hours/"
"Week`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ime`: Vnesite ime za novi privzeti delovni ńćas. To naj bo opisno "
"in jasno razumljivo, kot je `Standardnih 20 ur/teden`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:106
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Flexible Hours`: Check the checkbox to let employees adjust their "
"start and end times while maintaining the same total daily hours."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ProŇĺne ure`: Oznańćite potrditveno polje, da kadru omogońćite "
"prilagajanje zańćetnega in konńćnega ńćasa ob ohranitvi enake skupne dnevne "
"delovne obveze."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:108
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company Full Time`: Enter the number of hours per week an "
"employee needs to work to be considered a full-time employee. Typically, "
"this is approximately 40 hours, and this number affects what types of "
"benefits an employee can receive, based on their employment status (full-"
"time vs part-time)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Polni delovni ńćas podjetja`: Vnesite Ň°tevilo ur na teden, ki jih "
"mora zaposleni delati, da velja za zaposlenega s polnim delovnim ńćasom. "
"Obińćajno je to pribliŇĺno 40 ur in ta Ň°tevilka vpliva na vrste ugodnosti, ki "
"jih lahko zaposleni prejme, glede na njegov status zaposlitve (polni delovni "
"ńćas proti skrajŇ°anemu delovnemu ńćasu)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:112
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Average Hour Per Day`: Auto-populated based on the working hours "
"in the :guilabel:`Working Hours` tab. This entry affects resource planning "
"by determining how many resources can be used per workday."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Povpreńćno Ň°tevilo ur na dan`: Samodejno izpolnjeno na podlagi "
"delovnih ur v zavihku :guilabel:`Delovni ńćas`. Ta vnos vpliva na nańćrtovanje "
"virov z dolońćanjem, koliko virov je mogońće uporabiti na delovni dan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:115
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/working_schedules.rst:55
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Work Time Rate`: This percentage is auto-generated based on the "
"entry for the :guilabel:`Company Full Time` and the working hours configured "
"in the :guilabel:`Working Hours` tab. This number should be between `0.00%` "
