#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:127
msgid ""
"Each day includes morning (8:00‚Äď12:00), lunch (12:00‚Äď13:00), and afternoon "
"(13:00‚Äď17:00) periods, configured using the 24-hour time format."
