"opredeljujejo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:None
msgid "All available salary structures."
msgstr "Vse razpoloŇĺljive plańćne strukture."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:163
msgid ""
"Click on a structure to view its :guilabel:`Salary Rules`. These rules "
"define how the payslip will be computed for the employee."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na strukturo, da si ogledate njene :guilabel:`Plańćne pravila`. Ta "
"pravila dolońćajo, kako bo izrańćunan plańćni seznam za kadra."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:167
msgid ""
"After installing a :doc:`payroll localization <payroll_localizations>`, "
"relevant structures are installed and appear in this list."
msgstr ""
"Po namestitvi :doc:`lokalizacije plańćnega seznama <payroll_localizations>` "
"so ustrezne strukture nameŇ°ńćene in se prikaŇĺejo na tem seznamu."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:None
msgid ""
"Salary structure details for Regular Pay, listing all the specific Salary "
"Rules."
msgstr ""
"Podrobnosti plańćne strukture za redno plańćilo z navedbo vseh specifińćnih "
