"na podlagi njihove zaporedne Ň°tevilke. Pravila z niŇĺjo zaporedno Ň°tevilko se "
"izrańćunajo najprej, njihove rezultate pa lahko uporabijo pravila z viŇ°jo "
"zaporedno Ň°tevilko. To polje je **obvezno**."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salaries.rst:204
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Appears on Payslip`: Check the checkbox to have the rule visible "
"on the employee payslip PDF."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`PrikaŇĺi na plańćilni listi`: Oznańćite potrditveno polje, da bo "
