"samodejno poŇ°lje e-poŇ°tno sporońćilo z uporabo nastavljene, vnaprej "
"pripravljene predloge, takoj ko kartica kandidata vstopi v fazo. Ta "
"samodejno poslana e-poŇ°tna sporońćila so dolońćena v vsaki fazi poteka "
"kandidata."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/recruitment.rst:20
msgid ""
"The flow described in this document is Odoo's default configuration, but it "
"can be customized to suit any recruitment process."
