"ima vsako delovno mesto dolońćene :ref:`podrobnosti postopka <recruitment/"
"new_job_position/edit>`, ki navajajo ńćas, ki ga morajo kandidati prińćakovati "
"med dolońćenimi fazami."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/recruitment/velocity_analysis.rst:10
msgid ""
"Knowing how long applicants remain in each stage can help highlight possible "
"bottlenecks. Analyzing this data allows the recruitment team to assess each "
"stage, identify any issues, and pivot their strategies to move applicants "
"through each stage, within the expected time interval."
msgstr ""
"Poznavanje ńćasa, ki ga kandidati preŇĺivijo v vsaki fazi, lahko pomaga "
"izpostaviti morebitna ozka grla. Analiza teh podatkov omogońća kadrovski "
"ekipi, da oceni vsako fazo, prepozna morebitne teŇĺave in prilagodi svoje "
"strategije za premikanje kandidatov skozi vsako fazo v prińćakovanem ńćasovnem "
"intervalu."

