"email>`, :ref:`SMS <referrals/sms>`, :ref:`WhatsApp <referrals/"
"whatsapp>`, :ref:`sledilne povezave <referrals/link>` in "
"razlińćnih :ref:`platform druŇĺbenih medijev <referrals/social>`."

