msgstr ""
"Ustvariti je treba mejnike, da kader nabira odsotnost iz nańćrta nabiranja. "
"Vsak mejnik dolońća, kdaj in koliko odsotnosti kader zasluŇĺi."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/accrual_plans.rst:78
msgid ""
"To create a new milestone, click the :guilabel:`Create a milestone` button "
"and a *New Milestone* pop-up window loads. Then fill out the following "
"sections on the form."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje novega mejnika kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Ustvari mejnik` in "
