"vidijo :ref:`kdo jemlje odsotnost, koliko so jo porabili <time_off/by-"
"employee>`, :ref:`katere vrste se pogosteje uporabljajo <time_off/by_type>` "
"in :ref:`koliko ima vsak kader Ň°e na voljo <time_off/balance>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/reporting.rst:10
msgid ""
"Any report can be added to a spreadsheet, when in either the :icon:`fa-area-"
"chart` :guilabel:`(Graph)` or :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`(Pivot)` "
