"Omogońćite moŇĺnost :guilabel:`Dovoli negativno omejitev`, ńće naj bi kader "
"lahko zahteval veńć odsotnosti, kot jo trenutno ima, kar omogońća negativno "
"stanje. ńĆe je omogońćeno, se prikaŇĺe polje :guilabel:`do`. V to polje vnesite "
"najveńćjo dovoljeno kolińćino negativnega ńćasa v dnevih."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:176
msgid ""
"Sara currently has three days of the `Vacation` time off type. She is "
"planning a trip that requires five days of time off."
msgstr ""
"Sara ima trenutno na voljo tri dni vrste odsotnosti `Vacation`. Nańćrtuje "
"potovanje, ki zahteva pet dni odsotnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:179
msgid ""
"The `Vacation` time off type has the :guilabel:`Allow Negative Cap` option "
"enabled, and the :guilabel:`Maximum Excess Amount` is set to five."
msgstr ""
"Vrsta odsotnosti `Dopust` ima omogońćeno moŇĺnost :guilabel:`Dovoli negativno "
"omejitev` in :guilabel:`Najveńćji preseŇĺni znesek` je nastavljen na pet."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/time_off/time_off_types.rst:182
msgid ""
"These settings allow Sara to submit a request for five days of the "
"`Vacation` time off type. If approved, her `Vacation` time off balance will "
"be negative two (-2) days."
msgstr ""
"Te nastavitve Sari omogońćajo, da odda zahtevo za pet dni vrste odsotnosti "
"`Dopust`. ńĆe je odobrena, bo njeno stanje odsotnosti `Dopust` negativno dva "
